description: Lists the block lists used for query suggestions for an index. For information on the current quota limits for block lists, see Quotas for Amazon Kendra. ListQuerySuggestionsBlockLists is currently not supported in the Amazon Web Services GovCloud (US-West) region.

parameters.name: IndexId
parameters.description: The identifier of the index for a list of all block lists that exist for that index. For information on the current quota limits for block lists, see Quotas for Amazon Kendra.

nested_items.name: BlockListSummaryItems
nested_items.description: Summary items for a block list.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The identifier of a block list.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the block list.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the block list.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp when the block list was created.

nested_items.name: UpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp when the block list was last updated.

nested_items.name: ItemCount
nested_items.description: The number of items in the block list file.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon Kendra returns this token that you can use in the subsequent request to retrieve the next set of block lists.
